{"tid":1164151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣男童收晾衣物失足　4樓墮下跌斷腳","createTime":"2019-05-21T01:18:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T19:03:02.000Z","uid":20933,"like":168,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"781a4ac7b71694f986c36ff98fd28a99606a3f68","tid":1164151,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190521/large/1558400184_04e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190521%2Flarge%2F1558400184_04e6.jpg&h=7596a1a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早上8時許，荃灣川龍街135號一名12歲男童，由高處墮下，跌在大廈1樓簷篷，右腳骨折，痛極呼叫。<br />\n<br />\n救護員接報到場將男童送瑪嘉烈醫院搶救，警方初步調查顯示，他在4樓單位收晾衣物時意外墮下，現正封鎖現場了解事件。"},{"pid":"cde299da6acf7a789ab7992e9eba6de6a9f18f0e","tid":1164151,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:18:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190521/59623654\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190521%2F59623654&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbYeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=3aadb996\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190521%2F59623654&h=1b7130d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190521/59623654</a>"},{"pid":"b951c87f1781e61754f0be371e339fab540ddb25","tid":1164151,"uid":10692,"like":15,"dislike":89,"score":-74,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:18:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e5a7b5f8fa37ea856e302f32b28cb573e67e0603","tid":1164151,"uid":240762,"like":682,"dislike":3,"score":679,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:19:43.000Z","msg":"肯幫手收衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb039125bc472881d2b1a7a82d0d6f0bcf5667ab","tid":1164151,"uid":121546,"like":81,"disli